#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/index.rst:2
#: e7ba3e74c0914d0ba874affe3eb3b4ed
msgid "Solid Mechanics"
msgstr "固体力学"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/index.rst:4
#: e68cf17c677b49a28e5b614c73833fb3
msgid ""
"Four worked solid-mechanics examples in ``examples/solid/``, built as a "
"progressive ladder — each rung adds exactly one new concept on top of the "
"previous one:"
msgstr "``examples/solid/`` 中的四个固体力学完整示例，按照渐进的阶梯式组织——每一级都恰好在上一级之上增加一个新概念："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/index.rst:8
#: e0fdfb7a49114a7e9486fdbcca1208a4
msgid ""
"**Cantilever Beam** — linear elasticity, one direct solve. The baseline."
msgstr "**悬臂梁** —— 线弹性，一次直接求解。作为基线。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/index.rst:10
#: 26e449ed0e604d17bad591e0eb8f4198
msgid ""
"**Hyperelastic Beam** — finite strain (Neo-Hookean); introduces the L-BFGS "
"energy-minimization recipe."
msgstr "**超弹性梁** —— 有限应变（新胡克）；引入 L-BFGS 能量最小化方法。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/index.rst:12
#: 1ca80b173afc446c9b381022b233823b
msgid ""
"**Hertzian Contact** — adds a constraint (contact penalty) and a closed-form"
" verification, reusing the same L-BFGS recipe."
msgstr "**赫兹接触** —— 增加了一个约束（接触罚函数）和一个闭式解验证，复用同一套 L-BFGS 方法。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/index.rst:14
#: 860d8de59c1c4162b5f668bf4abc7ad1
msgid ""
"**Plasticity (J2)** — adds path-dependence: per-quadrature history variables"
" and a variational constitutive update, in 2D and 3D."
msgstr "**塑性（J2）** —— 增加了路径相关性：逐求积点的历史变量和变分本构更新，分别在二维和三维中实现。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/index.rst:18
#: 37ddee47191045aaa85a33a5050ea5f6
msgid ""
"Together they cover the two solver patterns TensorMesh uses for solid "
"problems:"
msgstr "它们合在一起涵盖了 TensorMesh 用于固体问题的两种求解模式："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/index.rst:21
#: 30b5eb9b03ca4e4bb2d74fc759690e65
msgid ""
"**Direct linear solve** for small-strain linear elasticity "
"(``cantilever_beam``)."
msgstr "**直接线性求解**\\ ，用于小应变线弹性（\\ ``cantilever_beam``\\ ）。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/index.rst:23
#: b695f9369853492199f5dfb3f369545d
msgid ""
"**L-BFGS energy minimization** for nonlinear problems where the potential "
"energy is well-defined — hyperelasticity, contact, and plasticity "
"(``hyperelastic_beam``, ``hertzian_contact``, ``plasticity_strip``)."
msgstr ""
"**L-BFGS 能量最小化**\\ ，用于势能有良好定义的非线性问题——超弹性、接触和塑性（\\ ``hyperelastic_beam``\\ "
"、\\ ``hertzian_contact``\\ 、\\ ``plasticity_strip``\\ ）。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/index.rst:28
#: e573fa8234c64a7ebb080754ec562e1a
msgid "The order below mirrors solver complexity."
msgstr "下面的顺序对应求解器复杂度的递增。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/index.rst:33
#: f9918fdea1d14b2ea5a739052db74900
msgid "Cantilever Beam"
msgstr "悬臂梁"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/index.rst:38
#: 097965d4324248dd8ed9250d1b4a0fb0
msgid ""
"Linear elasticity, steel cantilever with a tip load — the simplest end-to-"
"end recipe."
msgstr "线弹性，端部受载的钢制悬臂梁——最简单的端到端流程。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/index.rst:40
#: bf343b5c52fb4589acf9e9f7ce8c5a20
msgid "Hyperelastic Beam"
msgstr "超弹性梁"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/index.rst:45
#: 35bfe430e52841b788acbeee306f4b24
msgid ""
"Rubber beam under torsion, compressible Neo-Hookean, L-BFGS load stepping."
msgstr "扭转下的橡胶梁，可压缩新胡克，L-BFGS 载荷步进。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/index.rst:47
#: 0af782fecdce4117b5f8ab0ee626f229
msgid "Hertzian Contact"
msgstr "赫兹接触"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/index.rst:52
#: eed739db7cde4eaa9ac19451b8aa0a70
msgid ""
"Penalty contact between a circular indenter and an elastic block, checked "
"against the Hertz solution."
msgstr "圆形压头与弹性体之间的罚函数接触，并与赫兹解进行对照。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/index.rst:54
#: c7dc601db2ed4f83bd420436d9795ef7
msgid "Plasticity (J2)"
msgstr "塑性（J2）"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/index.rst:59
#: a1d139a4458749bc85a4549c1faa8c98
msgid ""
"Plane-strain J2 plasticity with isotropic hardening, load / unload cycle, "
"plus a 3D cube."
msgstr "带各向同性硬化的平面应变 J2 塑性，加载/卸载循环，外加一个三维立方体。"

